snippet.title: EtherOrcs Dungeons - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Realm of Valkala! Where magic still lives and The Orcs and their allies reside. 

Our new Dungeons mode is an active turn-based RPG with an extensive crafting system for strengthening your Horde to new limits.

Join the horde to farm $ZUG, Upgrade Your Gear via pillaging, fight other Orcs in PvP, and summon POWERFUL Allies to join your side. 

Everything is 100% on-chain and completely immutable. Live forever as a legend in VALKALA!

------------------------------------------------------ 

Play the Game: https://etherorcs.com/town

Check out more about Ether Orcs here: https://docs.etherorcs.com/main/ 

Linktree: https://linktr.ee/EtherOrcs

 

-------------------------------------------------------- 

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/EtherOrcs 

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/p7RdzvtM6U

 

#NFT #Orcs #onchaingaming
